{
  "texts": [
    "This study proposes combining the interval estimation algorithm to add an insurance policy to a trading strategy that can support significant improvement in trading returns under high volatility conditions.",
    "The innovation of this study lies in three aspects.",
    "First, the data are considered comprehensively.",
    "The data form includes time-series data and textual data; the data sources include news media, stock market experts, and the general public; and the data connotation includes stock characteristics, practitioner sentiment, and pandemic information.",
    "Second, this study makes innovative use of models."
  ]
}